msgctxt "Addon Summary"
msgid "PlayStation Dual Analog"
msgstr "PlayStation Dual Analog"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "The PlayStation controller was released by Sony Computer Entertainment in 1994. Sony briefly released the Dual Analog controller in 1997, followed by the rumble-enabled DualShock later that year."
msgstr "Ovladač PlayStation vydala společnost Sony Computer Entertainment v roce 1994. V roce 1997 společnost Sony krátce prodávala ovladač Dual Analog a později téhož roku následoval DualShock s podporou vibrací."

